  "root_text": {
    "kp8:0.1": "Khuddakapāṭha 8 ",
    "kp8:0.2": "Nidhikaṇḍasutta ",
    "kp8:1.1": "Nidhiṁ nidheti puriso, ",
    "kp8:1.2": "gambhīre odakantike; ",
    "kp8:1.3": "Atthe kicce samuppanne, ",
    "kp8:1.4": "atthāya me bhavissati. ",
    "kp8:2.1": "Rājato vā duruttassa, ",
    "kp8:2.2": "corato pīḷitassa vā; ",
    "kp8:2.3": "Iṇassa vā pamokkhāya, ",
    "kp8:2.4": "dubbhikkhe āpadāsu vā; ",
    "kp8:2.5": "Etadatthāya lokasmiṁ, ",
    "kp8:2.6": "nidhi nāma nidhīyati. ",
    "kp8:3.1": "Tāvassunihito santo, ",
    "kp8:3.2": "gambhīre odakantike; ",
    "kp8:3.3": "Na sabbo sabbadā eva, ",
    "kp8:3.4": "tassa taṁ upakappati. ",
    "kp8:4.1": "Nidhi vā ṭhānā cavati, ",
    "kp8:4.2": "saññā vāssa vimuyhati; ",
    "kp8:4.3": "Nāgā vā apanāmenti, ",
    "kp8:4.4": "yakkhā vāpi haranti naṁ. ",
    "kp8:5.1": "Appiyā vāpi dāyādā, ",
    "kp8:5.2": "uddharanti apassato; ",
    "kp8:5.3": "Yadā puññakkhayo hoti, ",
    "kp8:5.4": "sabbametaṁ vinassati. ",
    "kp8:6.1": "Yassa dānena sīlena, ",
    "kp8:6.2": "saṁyamena damena ca; ",
    "kp8:6.3": "Nidhī sunihito hoti, ",
    "kp8:6.4": "itthiyā purisassa vā. ",
    "kp8:7.1": "Cetiyamhi ca saṅghe vā, ",
    "kp8:7.2": "puggale atithīsu vā; ",
    "kp8:7.3": "Mātari pitari cāpi, ",
    "kp8:7.4": "atho jeṭṭhamhi bhātari. ",
    "kp8:8.1": "Eso nidhi sunihito, ",
    "kp8:8.2": "ajeyyo anugāmiko; ",
    "kp8:8.3": "Pahāya gamanīyesu, ",
    "kp8:8.4": "etaṁ ādāya gacchati. ",
    "kp8:9.1": "Asādhāraṇamaññesaṁ, ",
    "kp8:9.2": "acorāharaṇo nidhi; ",
    "kp8:9.3": "Kayirātha dhīro puññāni, ",
    "kp8:9.4": "yo nidhi anugāmiko. ",
    "kp8:10.1": "Esa devamanussānaṁ, ",
    "kp8:10.2": "sabbakāmadado nidhi; ",
    "kp8:10.3": "Yaṁ yadevābhipatthenti, ",
    "kp8:10.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:11.1": "Suvaṇṇatā susaratā, ",
    "kp8:11.2": "susaṇṭhānā surūpatā; ",
    "kp8:11.3": "Ādhipaccaparivāro, ",
    "kp8:11.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:12.1": "Padesarajjaṁ issariyaṁ, ",
    "kp8:12.2": "cakkavattisukhaṁ piyaṁ; ",
    "kp8:12.3": "Devarajjampi dibbesu, ",
    "kp8:12.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:13.1": "Mānussikā ca sampatti, ",
    "kp8:13.2": "devaloke ca yā rati; ",
    "kp8:13.3": "Yā ca nibbānasampatti, ",
    "kp8:13.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:14.1": "Mittasampadamāgamma, ",
    "kp8:14.2": "yonisova payuñjato; ",
    "kp8:14.3": "Vijjāvimuttivasībhāvo, ",
    "kp8:14.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:15.1": "Paṭisambhidā vimokkhā ca, ",
    "kp8:15.2": "yā ca sāvakapāramī; ",
    "kp8:15.3": "Paccekabodhi buddhabhūmi, ",
    "kp8:15.4": "sabbametena labbhati. ",
    "kp8:16.1": "Evaṁ mahatthikā esā, ",
    "kp8:16.2": "yadidaṁ puññasampadā; ",
    "kp8:16.3": "Tasmā dhīrā pasaṁsanti, ",
    "kp8:16.4": "paṇḍitā katapuññatanti. ",
    "kp8:17.1": "Nidhikaṇḍasuttaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "kp8:0.1": "Basic Passages 8 ",
    "kp8:0.2": "A Treasure Trove ",
    "kp8:1.1": "A person stores away their savings ",
    "kp8:1.2": "in a deep trove by the water’s edge: ",
    "kp8:1.3": "“When need arises ",
    "kp8:1.4": "it will be there to help ",
    "kp8:2.1": "free me from rulers if I am slandered, ",
    "kp8:2.2": "or from bandits if harassed, ",
    "kp8:2.3": "or to release me from debt, ",
    "kp8:2.4": "or in case of famine or losses.” ",
    "kp8:2.5": "What the world calls savings ",
    "kp8:2.6": "get stored away for such reasons. ",
    "kp8:3.1": "But no matter how well stored away they are ",
    "kp8:3.2": "in a deep pit by the water’s edge, ",
    "kp8:3.3": "all their savings will fail ",
    "kp8:3.4": "to aid them all the time. ",
    "kp8:4.1": "For perhaps those savings shift from there, ",
    "kp8:4.2": "or they forget what marks the site, ",
    "kp8:4.3": "or dragons make off with them, ",
    "kp8:4.4": "or spirits carry them away, ",
    "kp8:5.1": "or unloved heirs ",
    "kp8:5.2": "secretly unearth them. ",
    "kp8:5.3": "When their merit is used up, ",
    "kp8:5.4": "all of that will vanish. ",
    "kp8:6.1": "But by giving and morality, ",
    "kp8:6.2": "restraint and self-control, ",
    "kp8:6.3": "a woman or man ",
    "kp8:6.4": "keeps their savings safe. ",
    "kp8:7.1": "At a shrine or with the Saṅgha, ",
    "kp8:7.3": "with mother or father, ",
    "kp8:7.4": "or else an elder sibling, ",
    "kp8:8.1": "those savings are kept safe, ",
    "kp8:8.2": "they stay with you, undecaying. ",
    "kp8:8.3": "We must go on leaving all behind, ",
    "kp8:8.4": "only this you take when you go. ",
    "kp8:9.1": "You don’t have to share it with others, ",
    "kp8:9.2": "no thief makes off with your savings. ",
    "kp8:9.3": "An attentive one would make merit, ",
    "kp8:9.4": "the savings that stay with you. ",
    "kp8:10.1": "Such savings grant every desire ",
    "kp8:10.2": "of gods and humans too. ",
    "kp8:10.3": "Whatever it is that they wish for ",
    "kp8:10.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:11.1": "Good looks, a sweet voice, ",
    "kp8:11.2": "a good shape, and good appearance, ",
    "kp8:11.3": "leadership and followers: ",
    "kp8:11.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:12.1": "Sovereignty of a local kingdom, ",
    "kp8:12.2": "the happiness of a Wheel-Turning Monarch, ",
    "kp8:12.3": "even kingship in the heavens: ",
    "kp8:12.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:13.1": "Human success, ",
    "kp8:13.2": "heavenly delight, ",
    "kp8:13.3": "attaining extinguishment: ",
    "kp8:13.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:14.1": "Relying on having good friends, ",
    "kp8:14.2": "rational application of effort, ",
    "kp8:14.3": "mastery of knowledge and freedom: ",
    "kp8:14.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:15.1": "Analytical knowledge, the liberations, ",
    "kp8:15.2": "the perfections of the disciple, ",
    "kp8:15.3": "the plane of an independent Buddha: ",
    "kp8:15.4": "through this they have it all. ",
    "kp8:16.1": "This accomplishment in merit ",
    "kp8:16.2": "is so very beneficial. ",
    "kp8:16.3": "That’s why the attentive and the astute ",
    "kp8:16.4": "praise the making of merit. "
  },
